# Development Workflow

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repository
2. Install dependencies: `npm install`
3. Run development server: `npm run dev`

## Project Commands

- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run start` - Start production server
- `npm run lint` - Run linting

## Key Configuration Files

- [next.config.mjs](mdc:next.config.mjs) - Next.js configuration
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript configuration
- [postcss.config.mjs](mdc:postcss.config.mjs) - PostCSS configuration
- [app/auth.ts](mdc:app/auth.ts) - Authentication configuration

## Authentication Setup

- Authentication is implemented using NextAuth.js
- Login page is defined in [app/login/page.tsx](mdc:app/login/page.tsx)
- Setup auth provider in [app/components/AuthProvider.tsx](mdc:app/components/AuthProvider.tsx)

## Stack Overview

- Next.js 15.2.4
- React 19
- TypeScript 5
- Tailwind CSS 3.4.17
- NextAuth.js for authentication
- OpenAI API
- Lucide React (icons)
- Next Themes
- Zod (validation)